    "title": "Shock and awwwww! So cute!",
    "description": "Fires Shock projectiles in a high arc. Shots explode on impact, dealing 80% of bullet damage as splash in a small radius.\n\nOn kill: +70% cooldown rate for 6 seconds.\nOn critical kill: +130% cooldown rate for 6 seconds.\n\nAlways Shock. Increased damage, magazine size, and elemental chance."
  },
  "notes": "Rapidly swapping away from the gun and back after emptying the magazine can stack its effect, allowing extremely fast action skill recharge after kills.\n\nIt once featured as a guaranteed drop from Grendel during a limited-time event, alongside a hotfix that raised its damage and improved its action skill recharge bonus.\n\nIts 80% splash bonus is not increased by grenade damage boosts, unlike typical Maliwan splash interactions.",
